::Battera::

She awoke from her hybernation mode.  She unfolded her wings and 
stretched.  She yawned a bit and looked around the room.  She slowly 
sat up on the edge of her bed.  Sleeping for that long a time does 
make one a bit stiff in the joints.  She walked around her room a bit 
to wake up and walk out the stiffness.  She noticed that she wasn't 
called for. No one had come to her room to notify her of the leader 
returning to the base. She folded her wings behind her, opened he 
door to her room and walked out into the hallway.  She went along 
untill she came to the mess hall.  She went to the food dispencer and 
got a few items.  She sat down and munched on an apple.  She wondered 
what happened? Had the leader returned and just to busy to tak to 
her? Or had the leader returned at all?
